snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
We‚Äôre not done with you. #FNAF2movie in theaters December 5.

--

They‚Äôre not just at Freddy‚Äôs anymore. 
 
In 2023, Blumhouse‚Äôs box-office horror phenomenon Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs, based on the blockbuster game series by Scott Cawthon, became the highest-grossing horror film of the year. Now, a shocking new chapter of animatronic terror begins. 
 
One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear‚Äôs Pizza. The stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town‚Äôs first ever Fazfest. 
 
Former security guard Mike (Josh Hutcherson) and police officer Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) have kept the truth from Mike‚Äôs 11-year-old sister, Abby (Piper Rubio), concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. 
 
But when Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, it will set into motion a terrifying series of events, revealing dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy‚Äôs, and unleashing a long-forgotten horror hidden away for decades.
 
The cast of Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs 2 includes returning co-stars Theodus Crane as Jeremiah and the legendary Matthew Lillard as William Afton. The film features new characters played by Freddy Carter (Shadow and Bone, Pennyworth), Wayne Knight (Jurassic Park, Seinfeld), Mckenna Grace (Ghostbusters franchise, Annabelle Comes Home) and horror icon Skeet Ulrich (Scream, Riverdale). 
 
Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs 2 is directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Emma Tammi and is written by game series creator Scott Cawthon.
 
The film is produced by Blumhouse founder and CEO Jason Blum and Scott Cawthon, who together produced the first film. The executive producers are director Emma Tammi, Beatriz Sequeira, Christopher Warner, Russell Binder and Marc Mostman. 
 
The first Freddy‚Äôs film opened to a record-shattering $80 million in October 2023 and went on to earn almost $300 million worldwide.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Battlefield 6 - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare for the ultimate all-out warfare experience. Here's your look at the Battlefield 6 reveal trailer for the next game in the action FPS series. The Battlefield 6 announcement trailer shows chaos unfolding in cities and more. The trailer also unveils that a multiplayer reveal for Battlefield 6 is coming on July 31, 2025.

Check out the Battlefield 6 trailer's official description, which states, "Witness the vicious path of destruction carved by Pax Armata, the world‚Äôs leading private military company. PAX pursues the destruction of NATO and its allies, stopping at nothing to uphold their motto: ‚ÄúOur Protection, Your Peace.‚Äù

Lock & load for the ultimate all-out warfare experience. Fight in high-intensity infantry combat. Rip through the skies in aerial dogfights. Demolish your environment for a strategic advantage. In a war of tanks, fighter jets, and massive combat arsenals, your squad is the deadliest weapon. This is Battlefield 6."

#IGN #Battlefield #EA

snippet.title: One Battle After Another | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
No fear. #OneBattleAfterAnother only in theaters September 26.

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Academy Award-nominated, BAFTA-winning filmmaker Paul Thomas Anderson comes ‚ÄúOne Battle After Another,‚Äù starring Academy Award and BAFTA winner Leonardo DiCaprio.

Oscar and BAFTA winners Sean Penn and Benicio Del Toro also star alongside Regina Hall, Teyana Taylor and Chase Infiniti, as well as Wood Harris and Alana Haim.

Anderson directs from his own screenplay. The producers are Oscar and BAFTA nominees Adam Somner and Sara Murphy and Anderson, with Will Weiske executive producing.

The creative team behind the camera includes several frequent collaborators, among them directors of photography Michael Bauman and Anderson; Oscar-nominated, BAFTA-winning production designer Florencia Martin; BAFTA-nominated editor Andy Jurgensen; Oscar and BAFTA-winning costume designer Colleen Atwood; casting director Cassandra Kulukundis; and with music by Oscar- and BAFTA-nominated composer Jonny Greenwood.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A Ghoulardi Film Company Production, A Paul Thomas Anderson Film, ‚ÄúOne Battle After Another.‚Äù Distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures, the film will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on September 26, 2025, and internationally beginning 24 September 2025.

Tonton "THE EQUALIZER 4 ‚Äì Trailer Konsep Buatan Penggemar"

Dua legenda. Satu misi. Tanpa celah kesalahan.
Dalam trailer konsep buatan penggemar yang eksplosif ini, The Equalizer 4 mempertemukan Denzel Washington dan Jason Statham sebagai sekutu yang tak terduga dalam perlombaan melawan waktu untuk menghentikan Perang Dunia III. Ketika seorang dalang global yang kejam‚Äîdiperankan oleh Giancarlo Esposito‚Äîmelaksanakan rencananya, McCall harus bergabung dengan seorang mantan tentara bayaran yang mematikan untuk menghancurkan ancaman dari dalam.

Berani, intens, dan didorong oleh perhitungan moral, sekuel imajiner ini menyelami konspirasi global, pertempuran brutal, dan harga keadilan di dunia yang terpecah belah.

snippet.title: Code Violet - Release Date Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Visit the PlayStation Store to Pre-Order Now!
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012908

Code Violet: Survive the Horror, Unravel the Truth

Dive into Code Violet, an exhilarating third-person action horror game from TeamKill Media.
In the 25th century, a cataclysm has left Earth uninhabitable, driving humanity‚Äôs survivors to Trappist 1-E. Facing extinction due to sterility, the Aion colony harnesses cutting-edge time-travel technology to abduct women from the past to be surrogates in a dark yet desperate bid to save mankind.
But their mission conceals a sinister conspiracy. As Violet Sinclair, torn from your time, you awaken in the Aion Bioengineering Complex, swarming with ferocious prehistoric dinosaurs and hostile forces. Carefully manage your inventory, uncover Aion‚Äôs dark secrets, fight to survive, and escape during a chaotic evacuation protocol.

Can you save those you care for and make it out alive?


Features:

‚Ä¢ Heart-Stopping Survival Gameplay: Feel the panic as you outmaneuver relentless dinosaurs with scarce resources and stealth, delivering the intense panic horror you crave.

‚Ä¢ Strategic Inventory Management: Master limited inventory slots to prioritize weapons, healing items, and puzzle-solving tools, making every choice critical to surviving the complex‚Äôs deadly threats.

‚Ä¢ Explosive Action Horror Combat: Dive into thrilling third-person battles against savage dinosaurs, blending melee and ranged tactics for adrenaline-pumping encounters.

‚Ä¢ Stunning Ray-Traced Visuals with Unreal Engine‚Äôs Megalights: Lose yourself in haunting jungles and neon-lit facilities, where dynamic lighting, shadows, and reflections heighten the terrifying atmosphere.

‚Ä¢ Sony‚Äôs 3D Audio: Immerse yourself in a vivid soundscape where every rustle, roar, and echo brings jungles and facilities to life, amplifying tension with pinpoint directional audio.

‚Ä¢ Adaptive Triggers and Haptic Feedback: Experience every action‚Äîweapon recoil, evasion struggles, puzzle interactions, and combat impacts‚Äîthrough dynamic triggers and tactile feedback, making every move and solution visceral and impactful.

‚Ä¢ Gripping Conspiracy Narrative: Unravel a tale of betrayal tied to Aion‚Äôs time-travel tech and surrogate program, with Violet‚Äôs journey revealing shocking twists that keep you hooked.

‚Ä¢ Mind-Bending Puzzles: Solve intricate environmental and mechanical puzzles to unlock paths and secrets, adding depth and rewarding critical thinking for a satisfying challenge.

‚Ä¢ Terrifying Prehistoric Creatures: Confront intelligently designed beasts and classic dinosaurs that stalk unpredictably, blending nostalgia with cutting-edge AI for unforgettable chases.


Immerse yourself in a visually spectacular, heart-racing, panic filled adventure packed with survival horror, strategic inventory management, explosive action, and brain-teasing puzzles. Perfect for thrill-seekers and fans of dino-driven chaos.

#ps5 #ps5games

snippet.title: Past Life #3 - Secret Society Task
snippet.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.

localized.title: Past Life #3 - Secret Society Task
localized.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.

========= Lightning at the Gates LYRICS ==========

From the Rh√¥ne through the mountains they go

As the winter is drawing near, fast approaching change of season is threatening
March over mountains an army ascends

A threat to Rome comes from the north, through rocks they go

Over mountains, an army far from home
Leading beast and man through the cold and snow
Marching, they‚Äôre moving on Rome
Guided by the stars, light the valley below

As they cross the range where no armies go

From the peaks to the heart of their foe

Lead by Gauls to find the way, unite the tribes to show them through the mountains
Higher and higher, across the divide
Face the odds, the mountains‚Äô wrath, they took the unexpected path

========= Historic Fact ==========

Hannibal Barca, a Carthaginian general from North Africa, became one of Rome‚Äôs most formidable foes after the First Punic War. Determined to restore Carthage‚Äôs glory, he took command of its army at age 26 and led a daring invasion of Italy from Iberia, famously crossing the Alps with his army and 37 war elephants. Hannibal secured major victories at Trebia and Lake Trasimene, with his most famous success at the Battle of Cannae in 216 B.C., where he employed a masterful double envelopment to crush a much larger Roman force ‚Äì a tactic that‚Äôs still studied in military strategy today.

snippet.title: Devil's Ruin is BUSTED (Exotic Rework) | Destiny 2 Edge of Fate
snippet.description:
Today we are taking a look at one of our Exotic weapons that received a rework with Edge of Fate. Now, I expected Devil's Ruin to be pretty good after this rework but I did not expect this Exotic to be absolutely busted. On top of its rework, this weapon is benefiting from being a featured weapon, it has tons of artifact and subclass synergy, and there's currently a bug that makes this Exotic absolutely broken..

en.title: Devil's Ruin is BUSTED (Exotic Rework) | Destiny 2 Edge of Fate
en.description:
Today we are taking a look at one of our Exotic weapons that received a rework with Edge of Fate. Now, I expected Devil's Ruin to be pretty good after this rework but I did not expect this Exotic to be absolutely busted. On top of its rework, this weapon is benefiting from being a featured weapon, it has tons of artifact and subclass synergy, and there's currently a bug that makes this Exotic absolutely broken..

snippet.title: Crazy Train - Ozzy Osbourne (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Crazy Train - Ozzy Osbourne (Lyrics)

üîî Turn on notifications to stay updated with new uploads!

Lyrics:


[Intro]
All aboard, ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha
Ayy (Ayy, ayy, ayy, ayy, ayy, ayy)

[Verse 1]
Crazy, but that's how it goes
Millions of people living as foes
Maybe it's not too late
To learn how to love and forget how to hate

[Pre-Chorus]
Mental wounds not healing
Life's a bitter shame

[Chorus]
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train
(Let's go)

[Verse 2]
I've listened to preachers, I've listened to fools
I've watched all the dropouts, who make their own rules
One person conditioned to rule and control
The media sells it and you live the role

[Pre-Chorus]
Mental wounds still screaming
Driving me insane

[Chorus]
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train

[Bridge]
I know that things are going wrong for me
You gotta listen to my words, yeah, yeah

[Guitar Solo]

[Verse 3]
Heirs of a cold war, that's what we've become
Inheriting troubles, I'm mentally numb
Crazy, I just cannot bear
I'm living with something that just isn't fair

[Pre-Chorus]
Mental wounds not healing
Who and what's to blame?

[Chorus]
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train
I'm going off the rails on a crazy train

[Outro]
Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha
The ledge, ha-ha, the edge, edge

snippet.title: Alicia Keys - If I Ain't Got You
snippet.description:
Alicia Keys - If I Ain't Got You
Some people want it all, but I don't want nothing at all

Sundan si Alicia Keys

Lyrics:
[Panimula]
Mm-mm
Mm-mm, oh
Mm-mm

[Saknong]
Some people live for the fortune
Some people live just for the fame
Some people live for the power, yeah
Some people live just to play the game

[Pre-Koro]
Some people think that the physical things
Define what's within
And I've been there before, but that life's a bore
So full of the superficial

[Koro]
Some people want it all
But I don't want nothin' at all
If it ain't you, baby
If I ain't got you, baby
Some people want diamond rings
Some just want everything
But everything means nothin'
If I ain't got you, yeah

[Saknong]
Some people search for a fountain
That promises forever young (Ya know)
Some people need three dozen roses
And that's the only way to prove you love them

[Pre-Koro]
Hand me the world on a silver platter
And what good would it be?
With no one to share
With no one who truly cares for me

[Koro]
Some people want it all
But I don't want nothin' at all
If it ain't you, baby
If I ain't got you, baby
Some people want diamond rings
Some just want everything
But everything means nothin'
If I ain't got you, you, you
Some people want it all
But I don't want nothin' at all
If it ain't you, baby
If I ain't got you, baby
Some people want diamond rings
Some just want everything
But everything means nothin'
If I ain't got you, yeah

[Wakas]
If I ain't got you with me, baby
Oh, ooh
Said nothin' in this whole wide world don't mean a thing
If I ain't got you with me, baby

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

And let me tell you, some of the Discord features are complete money-grabs, some of them are sick, and a fair chunk of them are unequivocally mid. But there's one thing in common for these nitro features, shop features, server features, and potion features..... it's to make Discord money :)

snippet.title: Criticizing bad ideas from the DBD community
snippet.description:
In this video I'll be talking about a few very commonly suggested ideas that I don't think would be a good fit for DBD and explaing my reasoning as to why. Needless to say, everything in this video is just my personal opinion and you're more than free to disagree, especially if you leave a comment explaining your own thoughts!

00:00 Not all ideas are the same
01:35 "Make DBD free to play"
03:44 "Remove bloodpoint cap"
06:30 "Huge rewards for P100s"
08:15 "Crafting and/or reselling add-ons for BP "
10:30 "Make strong items very rare"
12:50 "Make all lobby backgrounds available"
14:10 "Reverse how map offerings work"
16:40 "Show who is in a SWF in the lobby" 
18:21 "Show who the Killer is in the lobby" 
20:25 "Just add a ranked mode" 
22:31 "Just add voice chat" 
26:57 "Just add basekit Corrupt Intervention" 
29:50 "Survivor specific buffs and/or limitations "
32:15 "Reset and/or move Hex Totems as Killer "
34:59 "Killswitch perks to spice up meta"
36:40 "Mori and/or instadown at gates"
38:37 "Perk idea: destroy/build breakable walls" 
39:59 "Perk idea: build pallets/walls" 
42:32 "Perk idea: fast vault from any angle"
44:33 "Balance idea: Make all Killers like Nurse"
47:07 "Balance idea: Survivors can't repeat perks"

51:32 "Balance idea - Make all Killers stealthy"
53:24 Final comments

snippet.title: The WORST Top Tier CAS Killer
snippet.description:
CAS planes have long reigned supreme in War Thunder's top tier ground battles, but that has changed with the addition of vehicles like the german IRIS-T and SLAMRAAM SPAA. The Swedish got the EldE 98, which is the worst top tier SPAA in the game. It has no range, no ammo, and no mobility. Rest assured, it dies to Su-34s and F-15s quite often.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.

Songs used (in order from first to last):
Halo OST
C&C: Generals Soundtrack

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/spookston

snippet.description:

Criken's second shift - https://youtu.be/QP6SBdym02s?si=FJerNeBs05t2jdhB

Jigsaw makeup and outro filming by plum ‚ù§

My links:
https://www.twitch.tv/charborg 
http://www.youtube.com/charborg 

Timestamps:
0:00 - Intro 
1:48 - First shift (Prepping the base for Criken)
4:52 - Second shift (Seeing what he got up to)

28:46 - Outro
